# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP Response Headers
# Applied at the CDN edge level on every response.
#
# frame-ancestors MUST be an HTTP header — browsers ignore it in <meta> CSP tags (W3C spec).
# X-Frame-Options is the legacy fallback for older browsers that don't support frame-ancestors.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'none'
